{"tid":2489744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"物理系畢業生被控突圍理大暴動 早前被鄭念慈撤銷保釋 還柙51日後今於區院獲准保釋 湯博士及舍監任擔保人","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:19:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"491726cc96dd236ae4f715955bb97c2df4141f9b","tid":2489744,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"前年「理大圍城」事件，一名就讀物理系的男生被指在科學館外攜有一個汽油彈，原被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪，直至今年2月尾，男生另被指從理大校園「突圍而出」，遭加控一項暴動罪，即時撤銷保釋，還柙至今已51日。現任職中大物理系活動主任的被告，今（15日）向區域法院申請保釋，法官李慶年聽取控辯雙方陳詞後，決定批出保釋。被告散庭後，向旁聽的朋友豎起姆指。<br />\n<br />\n被告由大律師黃瑞紅代表，獲准以3萬元保釋，中大物理系高級講師湯兆昇及宿舍舍監各以2萬元作人事擔保。被告在保釋期間不得離開香港、須交出旅遊證件包括BNO護照、每晚11時至翌日早上6時須守宵禁令、居於報稱住址及每周向警署報到4次。此外，其中一名擔保人須每天跟警方聯絡，確認被告仍在香港，若果擔保人與被告失去聯絡超過12小時，必須通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1082029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1082029&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=07db8367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1082029&h=a7643648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1082029</a>"},{"pid":"d2f3884b84acf9ffefee85daaedcc6ac5c76a05d","tid":2489744,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db980ed696fad258322f4cf57d0ab7c0c1aa0ac5","tid":2489744,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c64d9b7d29f48efdecbcc9e0404e640f5191e3d","tid":2489744,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeadd8e95e91acca5ebf1e7d6d7e87a0483782f","tid":2489744,"uid":185631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"做香港人唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n湯博士salute<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fea6e7b326ebbca60d9fb6fa19413f38c9c46d3","tid":2489744,"uid":213560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"手足加油！<br />\n<br />\n湯博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4b8261840689896f3e5ba46ccbc7f3b8e03601","tid":2489744,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"湯sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defca80bcf6dc5a933f50369c5281fd7ad275c73","tid":2489744,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"湯博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c332cd590e03b52ebb398bcd9c161bec8351819e","tid":2489744,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e5b94039c06fb8416ee4d04fada40572ee8788","tid":2489744,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"defca80bcf6dc5a933f50369c5281fd7ad275c73","tid":2489744,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"湯博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"佢好似已經做咗好多次擔保"},{"pid":"06373b0e61dda85dedad97c1a8a479ca69aaff06","tid":2489744,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"湯博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6d5f77b33190681e7449b868b7a847a86507dc","tid":2489744,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2330ac5e8d418fe317e3143ec65a30f3e5ab1bfb","tid":2489744,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"又唔承認BNO，但要人交出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac1cc9e5301a2c18155670447985796a313cfc1","tid":2489744,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"理工大學前年11月被警方連日圍堵，引發警民衝突。一名中文大學畢業生其間涉嫌管有汽油彈被捕，事隔逾年，今年初被加控暴動罪，並遭撤銷原有擔保。案件今於區域法院再提堂時，被告獲法官批准再度保釋。中大物理系高級講師「湯博士」湯兆昇願意擔任擔保人，他須每天與被告聯絡，並須向警員匯報及確認被告在港。案件押後至5月7日再訊。散庭時被告難掩喜悅，向旁聽席豎拇指和揮手。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今為被告向法庭提出保釋申請。法官李慶年接納申請，批准被告保釋候訊。被告獲兩名中大教職員任擔保人，包括中大物理系高級講師湯兆昇。其中一項保釋條件為湯須負責每天聯絡被告，並向指定警員匯報及確認被告在港；另外如跟被告失聯超過12小時，湯亦須即時通知警方。李官又特別提醒被告不要令擔保人失望，並指「若然潛逃會對佢哋（擔保人）好麻煩」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/Y2YXI7BZLJCUBMTWNS2CWYMOE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FY2YXI7BZLJCUBMTWNS2CWYMOE4%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=21fe0f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FY2YXI7BZLJCUBMTWNS2CWYMOE4%2F&h=acde8f0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/Y2YXI7BZLJCUBMTWNS2CWYMOE4/</a>"},{"pid":"e80c40e6c90859341ff24a75487c9100409610e4","tid":2489744,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"保釋左 會唔會走佬㗎？"},{"pid":"5fc9d3feef10038db2d2f38a444a497fb056f16a","tid":2489744,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"中大物理系活動主任<br />\n<br />\n高材生，入罪既話一定無得係學術界立足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2197da47c296ca1165f00611db78c6116b837d","tid":2489744,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"前年理大衝突，一名中文大學物理系畢業生被指管有汽油彈，一度遭還押，後來獲高等法院批准保釋。惟控方及後加控暴動罪，指他從校園「突圍而出」，裁判官撤銷擔保，他還押至今逾一個月。男學生今（15日）在區域法院申請保釋，並請來宿舍舍監和中大物理系高級講師、電視節目《學是學非》物理專家湯兆昇作其人事擔保。法官李慶年聽取陳詞後，批准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告今申請保釋，獲法官李慶年批准以 3 萬元保釋，中大物理系高級講師湯兆昇及宿舍舍監各以 2 萬元作人事擔保。保釋期間被告不得離開香港、須交出旅遊證件包括 BNO 護照、每晚 11 時至翌日早上 6 時宵禁、居於報稱住址及每周向警署報到 4 次。<br />\n<br />\n此外，其保釋條件要求其中一名擔保人須每天跟警方聯絡，確認被告在港，若擔保人與被告失去聯絡超過 12 小時，必須通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA-%E5%92%8C%E7%AE%A1%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592-%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%2580%258C%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=79bcb5d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592-%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%2580%258C%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B%2F&h=57aedafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA-%E5%92%8C%E7%AE%A1%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"91020980d5ab3355eb771bc2667b5426fbdf632f","tid":2489744,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}